Package: surfaceMetrics
Type: Incomplete Package
Title: Calculates surface metrics for raster layers
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Annalie Dorph
Maintainer: Annalie Dorph <adorph92@gmail.com>
Description: Employing gradient modelling techniques this code calculates 
     different surface metrics using rasters clipped to an area or as a 
     moving window analysis. The code for functions has been developed but
     it is not updated/ written to be employed as a package.

